ndmac.com/2019/10/ios-safarijingzhusongipdengsiliaoqudalijicidingbaopingan/</a><br />\n<br />\n報道指，原來在iOS系統設定中Safari有一項，預設會自動啟動網站安全檢查Fraudulent Website Warning，在當中有一項條款，寫明會向大陸騰訊傳送IP等私隱資料，以便成功作出檢查。據稱，要成功檢查用戶瀏覽的網站是否安全，大陸騰訊必然要知道用家正在瀏覽那一個網站。<br />\n<br />\n最恐怖的，是有關設定幾乎影響全球用戶，不只是香港或中國大陸而已。用家安裝其他瀏覽器亦未必能解決問題，因為蘋果強制App Store的瀏覽器使用WebKit引擎，亦即是說上述的系統設定有可能都套用至所有瀏覽器。<br />\n<br />\n目前唯一解決方法，是進入系統設定把其關閉。方法是按系統設定，選擇Safari，向下撥，找到如下圖把Fraudulent Website Warning詐騙網站警告關閉：<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/safari-settings-frau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2Fsafari-settings-frau.jpg&h=278fb065&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aefcc6326b2b082647b134f7ceaaccb3b1f12e88","tid":1652121,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:05:53.000Z","msg":"Safari冇乜人用"},{"pid":"10f55786cd681d97d08a88f3213ea7afad4b1923","tid":1652121,"uid":54153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c908096ef499c1a1a5ba9d6a12b15d89cb0bbac8","tid":1652121,"uid":54153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a47d535079fbe36af837b952682266f9e2e3022","tid":1652121,"uid":130595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aefcc6326b2b082647b134f7ceaaccb3b1f12e88","tid":1652121,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:05:53.000Z","msg":"Safari冇乜人用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"無得你唔用<br />\napp 裡面開親web view / browser 都只會係safari"},{"pid":"7c27520ab546aac47c89107d1048039bc2307f20","tid":1652121,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"check ed"},{"pid":"5017d732fccdc415755fac5be3b877cf1c823785","tid":1652121,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci